<p>If you want to check if an element is visible on the page, depending on the visibility of its parent, you can check if <code>width</code> and <code>height</code> of the element are both equal to <code>0</code>.</p>

<p>jQuery</p>

<p><code>$element.width() === 0 &amp;&amp; $element.height() === 0</code></p>

<p>Vanilla</p>

<p><code>element.clientWidth === 0 &amp;&amp; element.clientHeight === 0</code></p>

<p>Or</p>

<p><code>element.offsetWidth === 0 &amp;&amp; element.offsetHeight === 0</code></p>
